<p><i><b>The Amityville Horror - A True Story</b></i> is a best-selling book written by <a href="/wiki/Jay_Anson" title="Jay Anson">Jay Anson</a>, and published in September 1977. It is also the basis of a series of films released between 1979 and 2005. The book is said to be based on actual <a href="/wiki/Paranormal" title="Paranormal">paranormal</a> events, but has led to <a href="/wiki/Controversy" title="Controversy">controversy</a> and <a href="/wiki/Lawsuit" title="Lawsuit">lawsuits</a> over its truthfulness.<sup id="cite_ref-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-0" title=""><span>[</span>1<span>]</span></a></sup></p>
