<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=The_Amityville_Horror&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9" title="Edit section: Further reading">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Further reading</span></h2>
<ul>
<li>Holzer, Hans: <i>The Amityville Curse: Fact or Fiction?</i> (This is a 2007 reprint of <i>Murder in Amityville</i>, <i>The Amityville Curse</i> and <i>The Secret of Amityville</i>) <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/9780760785355" class="internal">ISBN 9780760785355</a></li>
<li>Kaplan, Stephen and Roxanne Salch: <i>The Amityville Horror Conspiracy</i> (1995) <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/9780963749802" class="internal">ISBN 978-0963749802</a></li>
<li>Osuna, Ric: <i>The Night the DeFeos Died</i> (2002) <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/9781591095866" class="internal">ISBN 978-1591095866</a></li>
</ul>
